{"tid":1928082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［立法會選舉］功能比泛民 地區留本土","createTime":"2020-03-16T07:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:01:18.000Z","uid":89353,"like":19,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"372fd6b8a85c5fc841b790ce885c64707ad76c5b","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">功能比泛民 地區留本土</span></span></strong><br />\n依個係一個策略性嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">根本如果地區係泛民為先票數可能會冇咁多<br />\n一，有一班人就係只投本土唔投泛民<br />\n二，香港人要嘅係改變 你留返低原本嗰班人會有咩改變<br />\n三，佢哋根本有班人仲係相信香港法治冇問題跟隨中國取得民主或者係中國入邊取得民主係冇問題<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">而點解留返功能直選超區比佢哋<br />\n原因好簡單<br />\n一，自己整出嚟嘅屎自己食返<br />\n二，坦白講本土真係冇咁多資源</span><br />\n<br />\n你可能會有以下幾個問題<br />\n一，淨係初選咪搞得掂囉<br />\n二，真本土一定會被DQ<br />\n<br />\n首先初選有咩問題，初選本來就會存在缺陷以上一次區議會選舉為例，個大台係民主黨結果係選舉裏面一啲本土因為得唔到認可而被DQ。換句說話來講如果初選係由傳統泛民組成結果本土嘅人唔會去投票或者根本參選唔到初選。<br />\n<br />\n而真本土一定會DQ，呢句說話我部份認同嘅。<br />\n如果你港獨一定會DQ，但坦白講冇得將本土定義標準設立到咁高先。如果你有留意傳統泛民或者新政黨既黨章或者理念你會留意到有好多政黨都會提及到自決無論係民主自決定民族自決。亦有好多仲係相信可以係中共下得到民主以香港是中國不可分割的一部份為第一信念。<br />\n加上周庭之前都上訴成功左，有機會部份自決可以留低。<br />\n<br />\n我認為可以有呢啲建議：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.建立初選<br />\n2.初選由政治光譜處於本土同傳統泛民中間嘅政黨組成<br />\n3.傳統泛民尤其是香港民主最大黨首先要分配好人手打功能組別之後先攻地區直選<br />\n4.本土要參選地區直選，如果準確啲來講係儘量只有本土參選<br />\n5.初選學雷動計劃話齋淨係合併成為一個政黨一個選擇</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9acfba12918a4e973e7f3951c5cd7288e7dee8ee","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"88af7c9b99da9141dde0d9603276703371b5aa47","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"cded3c7a37c07b740af049d92853d51d08455fa2","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ff5e0a44ea606bfa0e570674d6c86f48f3aef70b","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"a1a7459384ac97fe4dfef3d9117fc7dc951fae8e","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9478c6981432eaf1a0fc0eef58c6777de8f0e8","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07b6db2edcc99a750d9d9f0c6f49a0c63653174","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a51a2e61acb47c047aadff2e83304cc439caf3","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"8/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5fd20f66899768c457b70865cabf407e3ab709","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"9/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2829f483361928f062a5f6cff19a9d21c9710db","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"25ce11924ad19067e2d35ca7b6c0ab2e53f0571a","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4ae410afb5708f92803b66ae678808905203a5","tid":1928082,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372fd6b8a85c5fc841b790ce885c64707ad76c5b","tid":1928082,"uid":89353,"like